test:

    - gtk-encode-symbolic-svg --help
    - gtk-launch --help
    - gtk-query-immodules-3.0
    - gtk-update-icon-cache --help
    - gtk-query-settings
    - command -v gtk-builder-tool
    - test -f $PREFIX/include/gail-3.0/libgail-util/gail-util.h
    - test -f $PREFIX/include/gtk-3.0/gdk/gdk.h
    - test -f $PREFIX/include/gtk-3.0/gtk/gtk.h
    - test -f $PREFIX/include/gtk-3.0/unix-print/gtk/gtkunixprint.h
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/pkgconfig/gail-3.0.pc
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/pkgconfig/gdk-3.0.pc
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/pkgconfig/gtk+-3.0.pc
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/pkgconfig/gtk+-unix-print-3.0.pc
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/pkgconfig/gdk-quartz-3.0.pc
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/pkgconfig/gtk+-quartz-3.0.pc
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/libgailutil-3${SHLIB_EXT}
    - test -f `pkg-config --variable=libdir --dont-define-prefix gail-3.0`/libgailutil-3${SHLIB_EXT}
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/libgdk-3${SHLIB_EXT}
    - test -f `pkg-config --variable=libdir --dont-define-prefix gdk-3.0`/libgdk-3${SHLIB_EXT}
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/libgtk-3${SHLIB_EXT}
    - test -f `pkg-config --variable=libdir --dont-define-prefix gtk+-3.0`/libgtk-3${SHLIB_EXT}
    - test -f $PREFIX/share/glib-2.0/schemas/gschemas.compiled
    - test -f $PREFIX/share/icons/hicolor/icon-theme.cache
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/gtk-3.0/3.0.0/immodules.cache
  requires:
    - pkg-config
    - pygobject
  script: run_test.py

  description: 'GTK is a multi-platform toolkit for creating graphical user interfaces.

    from small one-off projects to complete application suites.

  license_family: LGPL
  license_file: COPYING
  summary: Version 3 of the Gtk+ graphical toolkit
